c: 39
v: 8
t: "Si loraa memii ne…ó…óo on, o noddira Joomi makko, ruttagol e Makko. Refti si O okkii mo mo∆¥∆¥ere, immorde ka Makko, o yejjita ko o noddaynoo kon ado …óum, o wa…óana Allah kafidii…ói, fii no o majjinira (yim…ìe …ìen) e laawol Makko ngol. MaAku: \"Dakmitor keeferaaku maa ngun, see…óa. Pellet, ko a jeyaa…óo e yim…ìe Yiite …ìen"